* **Chair's Update:** Mallory Knodel opened the meeting using the [Chair's Welcome Slides](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-hrpc-chairs-welcome-slides-00). She reminded participants of the IRTF’s Note Well, intellectual property rights, and code of conduct policies.
